# ClearFuneralCosts Migration Rules

## Project Context
This is a funeral cost analysis platform with:
- Static HTML pages converting to React/Next.js
- Existing color scheme: navy-primary (#1e3a8a), sage-green (#10b981)
- Responsive design with mobile-first approach
- Form validation and analytics integration

## Component Structure
- Break HTML into logical React components
- Maintain existing CSS class naming conventions
- Use TypeScript interfaces for props
- Keep existing responsive design patterns

## Styling Guidelines  
- Convert existing CSS to Tailwind classes
- Preserve color variables: navy-primary, sage-green, cream-bg
- Maintain 44px minimum touch targets for mobile
- Keep existing font stack: Georgia serif

## API Integration
- Use Supabase for database operations
- Implement n8n webhooks for data processing
- Add Stripe integration for payments
- Use React Query for data fetching